text: Stagecoach Buckaroo is a 1942 American Western film directed by Ray Taylor and written by Al Martin. The film stars Johnny Mack Brown, Fuzzy Knight, Nell O'Day, Anne Nagel, Herbert Rawlinson and Glenn Strange. The film was released on February 13, 1942, by Universal Pictures. ==Plot== ==Cast== *Johnny Mack Brown as Steve Hardin *Fuzzy Knight as Clem Clemmons *Nell O'Day as Molly Denton *Anne Nagel as Nina Kincaid *Herbert Rawlinson as Bill Kincaid *Glenn Strange as Breck Braddock *Henry Hall as Joseph Denton *Ernie Adams as Blinky *Lloyd Ingraham as Ezra Simpson *Frank Brownlee as Higgins *Jack C.
